    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "With this proposal we should be able to:\r\n- create an autocomplete experience using raw widgets\r\n- display hits from multiple indexes\r\n- connect any autocomplete like component (with connectMultiHits)\r\n\r\nThe API seems complex but I can't imagine any other nice proposal for now so let's go forward. @mikaa123 I do also like yours but I find the one from @mthuret more flexible. having to re-state the indexName everywhere is nesting (or context) but in a more repetitive way maybe..",
